quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  11,110,"Ni$, s tidep, Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Mgarraden fellas. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal s$uô Mass ik, yili useyyi garasen. Haaten, ih, di ccekk imcebbwel fellas"
  11,111,"War ccekk, akken ma llan, ad Ikafi Mass ik igiten nnsen, s lmizan. Neppa, s tidep, Issen ayen xeddmen"
  11,112,"Ihi, ili d uwqim, akken i k ippunefk lameô, keçç akked wid isteôoâen yidek. Ur be$wvet. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali ay txeddmem"
  11,113,"Ur pqeôôibet ar wid idensen, a kwen tnal tmes! Ur tesâim bab, war Öebbi, ihi, ur tepwasellkem"
  11,114,"èéal ûbeê, tameddit, kra n lewqat n yiv. S tidep, ise$iyen neqqven tucmitin. Ayagi d asmekti i wid ismektayen"
  11,115,"Eûbeô! Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iveggiâ taqdiât n lâuûam"
  11,116,"A lemmer llan, di tsuta i kwen id izwaren, imezgiyen ineqqven asefsed di tmurt! Qlilit kan seg wid Nsellek segsen. Wid idensen ddan akked wayen i ten izhan, u$alen d ibe$wviyen"
  11,117,"Ur Isquccu ara Mass ik timdinin, d aêerfi, ma llan imezda$ nnsent d lâuûam"
  11,118,"Lemmer i S ihwi i Mass ik, ad Irr imdanen d yiwen n lois. Zgan mgarraden"
  11,119,"Kkes ed wid i$ef Iêun Mass ik. Ixelq iten i wayagi. Itam wawal n Mass ik: \"ad Acaôe$ Loahennama, war ccekk, s leonun akked yimdanen mejmulen"
  11,120,"Ayen akw i k ed Neêka n tmucuha imazanen, iwakken a Ntebbet ul ik, yissent. Id iusan dagi d tidep, d anabi u d asmekti i lmumnin"
  11,121,"Ini i wid ur numin ara: \"xedmet ay tzemrem, nekwni s tidep, la nxeddem"
  11,122,"Gganit, nekwni la nepgani"
  11,123,"N Öebbi tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. £uôeS ara u$alen akw lumuô. Ihi, âabed iT, ppkel fellaS. Ur I$effel ara Mass ik, $ef wayen txeddmem"